1-1+1-1+\cdots=\frac{1}{2}
1+2+3+\cdots = -\frac{1}{12}
1+\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{3}+\cdots
 \lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}\frac{1}{m}\sum_{k=1}^{m}\sum_{n=1}^{k}\frac{1}{n} =\lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}\frac{1}{m}\sum_{k=1}^{m}H_{k}=\lim_{m\rightarrow\infty}\frac{1}{m}\left(m+1\right)\left(H_{m+1}-1\right)=\infty 
